      <event start="T536" end="T537">[glas] ej, </event>
      <event start="T537" end="T538">jaz sem tako vesela, </event>
      <event start="T538" end="T1743-497">k si danes prišla. </event>
      <event start="T1744-448" end="T1747-507">Tako da ... [smeh] </event>
      <event start="T1747-507" end="T539">Ja. </event>
      <event start="T539" end="T540">Jaz predlagam, da midve greva kar zdajle po indukcijo </event>
      <event start="T540" end="T1752-243">pa jo damo v avto, </event>
      <event start="T1752-243" end="T1752-778">da ne bomo slučajno res pozabile, </event>
      <event start="T1752-778" end="T566">pa da ne boš potem ti lačna, k ne bo, </event>
      <event start="T566" end="T1759-574">pa otroci, pa mož, pa vsi, </event>
      <event start="T1759-574" end="T1761-417">ker ne boš mogla skuhati. </event>
      <event start="T1762-13" end="T1763-498">Tako da to je to. </event>
      <event start="T1763-498" end="T541">Ej, </event>
      <event start="T541" end="T1765-895">ful ti hvala, ko si prišla. </event>
      <event start="T1765-895" end="T1767-322">Hmm? </event>
      <event start="T1767-322" end="T1768-65">Pa greva zdajle dol. </event>
      <event start="T1769-363" end="T543">Ja, </event>
      <event start="T543" end="T1771-404">ajde. </event>
    </tier>
